错误的response http code 列表：
200: 返回的正常的数据列表，单个对象或者数组对象

		单个对象
		{
		    "username": "网二",
		    "realname": "测试姓名2",
		    "phone_country": "",
		    "phone": "18618162135",
		    "type": 2,
		    "type_status": 0,
		    "is_test": 0
		}

		//数组对象
		[
		    {
		        "username": "网二",
		        "realname": "测试姓名2",
		        "phone_country": "",
		        "phone": "18618162135",
		        "type": 2,
		        "type_status": 0,
		        "is_test": 0       
		    },
		    {
		        "username": "5549",
		        "realname": "测试姓名5",
		        "phone_country": "",
		        "phone": "0",
		        "type": 0,
		        "type_status": 0,
		        "is_test": 0  
		    }

		    ...
		]


422: 表示数据验证错误
	格式如下
	[
	    {
	        "field": "bank_type",
	        "message": "开户行不能为空。"
	    },
	    {
	        "field": "bank_number",
	        "message": "开户账号不能为空。"
	    }
	]



	{
		1:[
			{
		        "field": "bank_type",
		        "message": "开户行不能为空。"
		    },
		    {
		        "field": "bank_number",
		        "message": "开户账号不能为空。"
		    }
	    ],
		5:[]
		...
	}
其他的状态返回一下格式： code 默认错误的状态码为0， 业务状态码单独指定

401：表示未通过验证
{"code":0,"message":"Your request was made with invalid credentials. from CRM-API"}

404： 没找到内容

{"code":0,"message":"\u6ca1\u53d1\u73b0 from CRM-API"}

400: 错误的请求  throw new BadRequestHttpException("错误的请求");
{"code":2000,"message":"\u6ca1\u53d1\u73b0 from CRM-API"}

500: 服务器内部错误  throw new \yii\web\ServerErrorHttpException('设置成功',code码);
{"code": code码 ,"message":"\u6ca1\u53d1\u73b0 from CRM-API"}

